HEADWORD: Musciform
<hw>Mus"ci*form</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Musca</ets>
+ <ets>-form</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Having the form or
