==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Musciform
<hw>Mus"ci*form</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Muscus</ets> +
<ets>-form</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Having the appearance or
form of a moss.</def>⟦br⟧
